    "description": "The goblins have stolen the gold collected in taxes from the villagers, and they have decided to hire a brave adventurer to recover it. Will you be the one to accomplish it?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWelcome to this casual action Roguelike, where the main objective is to retrieve the chest and return it to the villagers, but there are more challenges to face:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHow quickly can you recover it?<br />\r\nWill you be able to eliminate all the goblins in their lair?<br />\r\nAnd the King, can you defeat him?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe goblins have infested the caves with dangerous traps, and they themselves are very deceitful.<br />\r\nYou will have to use the few weapons available to you in the small shop set up by the villagers at the entrance of the dungeon.<br />\r\nThe gold you can steal from these wretched green skins can be spent at this shop, but some weapons, although powerful, are fragile and will break with use. But don't worry! You can return to the shop whenever you want to replenish them.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGo ahead and return the cursed gold!",
